{"tid":1050881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警車逆線行　車場連掃3架車　只因想掉頭？","createTime":"2019-03-07T07:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T08:00:44.000Z","uid":225464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"143a73034e8f319f8c4dde9ee30308c5da068c2f","tid":1050881,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:32:02.000Z","msg":"警車逆線行 車場連掃3架車 只因想掉頭？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190307/bkn-20190307123435389-0307_00822_001.html?refer=hn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190307%2Fbkn-20190307123435389-0307_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=9aadc0ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190307/bkn-20190307123435389-0307_00822_001.html?refer=hn2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190307/photo/bkn-20190307123435389-0307_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190307125055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190307%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190307123435389-0307_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190307125055&h=0b307c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n躺着也中槍？<br />\n<br />\n人有錯手，警有失蹄？有網民將天眼片段上載至Facebook群組「的士司機資訊網 Taxi」，星期二（5日）下午3時許，有警車在停車場連掃三架私家車，惹來一眾網民嘲笑︰「阿Sir撞車唔使你教」。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該警車隸屬將軍澳警區，當時有警員駕車在魷魚灣村道一帶巡邏，期間駛入附近一個停車場掉頭時，意外衝向停泊於車場內的私家車。<br />\n<br />\n從片段所見，當時警車在停車場內逆線行駛，擦過私家車後，曾扭軚轉向，惟意外再撞向旁邊兩架私家車始停下。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民揶揄︰「阿Sir你個牌點考番嚟㗎」、「香港腳發作」、「衝鋒車，唔衝就對唔住個名啦」、「X到冇朋友」。<br />\n<br />\n警方回應查詢指，事件中無人受傷，案件列作「交通意外無人受傷」處理，並已聯絡受影響的三名車主，積極跟進事件。"},{"pid":"ead0c94fbab53aa91c172c4b9e17f86a22168a56","tid":1050881,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:33:49.000Z","msg":"高層又震怒"},{"pid":"d445710ea6cdb9f780111b2f5a6c85875534c78b","tid":1050881,"uid":225464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:36:28.000Z","msg":"這是正式錄用的警察嗎？"},{"pid":"6e83e3910e1ef29b0bcf82fe7496dca3f25b6c4e","tid":1050881,"uid":42044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"車主搞上庭告佢啦，唔好俾佢賠錢了事呀。<br />\n<br />\n都話黑警實犯法  最大犯罪集團。<br />\n<br />\n藍絲狗出沒注意"},{"pid":"a9a70fb5ab1bb474eb978daa18de3dda93ceea96","tid":1050881,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T08:00:44.000Z","msg":"CLS點考牌?"}]}